		"description": "<p>Stealth, negotiations or combat, you&rsquo;re ready for anything. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You gain proficiency with a skill or tool of your choice.</li>\n<li>You gain learn Thieves&rsquo; Cant as if you had the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-backgrounds.Item.pvr4i8s3zkuroeuc]{Criminal} background. If you already know Thieves&rsquo; Cant, you learn a language of your choice instead.</li>\n<li>Half your scholar levels count as rogue levels for the purpose of the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.0k3qurx2exzg127v]{Shrewd Judgment} feature.</li>\n<li>Half your rogue levels count as scholar levels for the purpose of the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.luapp6zqydhkeemn]{Defensive Studies} feature.</li>\n<li>Half your rogue levels count as scholar levels for the purpose of the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.m36tik3n2m6qa4ci]{Wandering Sage} feature.</li>\n<li>You gain proficiency with a weapon of your choice that has the finesse and/or stealthy property.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>",
